    "description": {
      "zh": "用于装载超大、超重设备，并带有COMM 3电台背包的特殊装备。\nCOMM 3适配PRC117F/G、PRC119F、152/ASIP电台。如有需要，也可以用它单独收纳其他装备。模块化的NICE COMM3系统能够应对各种任务。\n这是一件极其稀有的装备，有人为了得到他，在塔科夫四处搜索。",
      "en": "The NICE Frame special system for carrying oversized or heavy loads with an installed COMM 3 backpack for carrying radio systems. The COMM 3 main bay is designed for PRC117F or G, PRC119F, 152, or ASIP radios. The Hitchhiker and Daypack lid allows you to carry separate gear if needed. The modular NICE COMM 3 system is ready to adapt to changing tasks. An extremely rare thing, for which a real hunt is conducted in Tarkov."
    },
